<div class="page-apply"><div class="container"><div class="apply-panel"><div class="apply-header"><a class="pull-left" href="#/home"><img src="images/7e31a229.in_logo.png" alt="logo"></a> <i class="pull-left"></i><span class="pull-left">注册</span></div><div ng-if="!success"><div class="title"><h4>注册</h4><p class="text-muted small">您需要填写以下资料，请务必提供真实数据，带星号的为必填项。</p></div><form role="form" name="applyForm" class="form-horizontal" ng-submit="apply()" novalidate><!-- 必填部分 --><div class="form-group"><label for="inputCompany" class="control-label">企业名称<i class="required-state is-required">*</i></label><input ng-change="resetError()" class="form-control" ng-model="company.name" type="text" maxlength="20" required placeholder="请输入企业名称（2－20个字符）"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="control-label">公司所在地<i class="required-state is-required">*</i></label><select class="form-control pull-left" ng-model="user.province" ng-options="address.name for address in addresses" ng-change="user.city = null"><option value="">省份</select><select class="form-control pull-left" ng-model="user.city" ng-options="city.name for city in user.province.citys"><option value="">城市</select></div><div class="form-group"><label class="pull-left control-label">联系人姓名<i class="required-state is-required">*</i></label><input ng-change="resetError()" class="form-control" ng-model="company.contact" type="text" required maxlength="10" placeholder="请输入姓名（1-10个字符）"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="pull-left control-label">手机号码<i class="required-state is-required">*</i></label><input ng-change="resetError()" class="form-control" ng-model="company.tel" type="text" maxlength="11" required placeholder="请输入11位手机号码"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="pull-left control-label">密码<i class="required-state is-required">*</i></label><input ng-change="resetError()" class="form-control" type="password" ng-model="company.password" name="password" maxlength="32" required placeholder="请输入密码（6-32位）"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="pull-left control-label">确认密码<i class="required-state is-required">*</i></label><input ng-change="resetError()" class="form-control" type="password" ng-model="check.repeatPassword" name="passwordConfirm" required maxlength="32" placeholder="请再次输入密码"></div><!-- 可选填写部分 --><div class="form-group"><label class="pull-left control-label">公司规模<i class="required-state">*</i></label><select class="form-control staffsize pull-left" ng-model="company.staffsize" ng-options="staffsize.id as staffsize.name for staffsize in staffsizes"><option value="">请选择公司规模</select></div><div class="form-group"><label class="pull-left control-label">联系人邮箱<i class="required-state">*</i></label><input ng-change="resetError()" class="form-control" ng-model="company.email" type="text" placeholder="您的邮箱"></div><!-- 用户协议，提交 --><div class="checkbox agreement"><label class="text-muted small"><input ng-change="resetError()" type="checkbox" name="check" ng-model="check.agreement" required>我已经认真阅读并同意{{logoName}}的<a target="_blank" href="#/protocol">《用户协议》</a></label></div><div class="alert alert-danger ng-class:{'hidden':!errorMessage}">{{errorMessage}}</div><button type="submit" class="btn btn-success" title="阅读并同意{{logoName}}的《使用协议》方可注册。" ng-disabled="waiting">提交申请</button> <img class="waiting-gif ng-class:{'hidden':!waiting}" src="images/a916fc6c.waiting.gif" alt="提交中"></form></div><div ng-if="success" class="success"><div class="center-image"><img src="images/e09b6397.apply_success.png"></div><p class="center-block signup-success">注册成功，您现在可以<a href="{{host}}/ems">登录</a>并管理您的企业信息。</p><a href="#/home" class="btn center-block">返回首页</a></div></div></div></div>